-----------------------------
|   DATABASE API ROUTES:    |
-----------------------------

*All tables have the same operations -> GET ALL, CREATE, GET BY ID, UPDATE BY ID, DELETE

example for user accounts:

  GET ALL - Obtain all user accounts: 
      GET http://localhost:3000/users 

  CREATE - Create a new user account: 
      POST http://localhost:3000/users 
      req.body all the information necessary for the creation (user_id, username, password, email)

  GET BY ID - Get user account by user_id:
      GET http://localhost:3000/users/user_id

  UPDATE BY ID - Update information about a a user account identifyed by user_id:
      PUT http://localhost:3000/users/user_id 
      req.body all the information necessary for the update (user_id, username, password, email)

  DELETE - Delete user account:
      DELETE http://localhost:3000/users
